**Animecraft RPG** is a fully custom **Warcraft III Reforged** map merging multiple anime universes into one connected world.  
You awaken as a lost soul in **HFIL** â€” the â€œHome For Infinite Losersâ€ â€” after the catastrophic **Great Convergence** tore rifts across worlds.  
